( door opens, closes )

25:53.519 --> 25:56.956
Adam:
HEY. HEY!

25:58.124 --> 26:00.893
COME WITH ME, KID.

26:04.997 --> 26:06.966
A-- ADAM.

26:09.501 --> 26:13.172
- ( distant siren blaring )
- THIS IS LIKE WHEN MY PARENTS
WOKE ME UP DURING A TORNADO.

26:13.272 --> 26:14.774
Adam:
JUST A LITTLE FARTHER.

26:14.874 --> 26:18.745
ADAM, I'M TIRED
AND I DON'T KNOW
WHERE WE'RE GOING.

26:20.747 --> 26:24.684
- Adam: SORRY I YELLED
AT THAT CAR.
- WHAT?

26:24.784 --> 26:26.786
I WISH I COULD APOLOGIZE,
BUT I DON'T KNOW THE DRIVER,

26:26.886 --> 26:30.222
