26:43.502 --> 26:46.105
( Hannah laughing )

26:46.205 --> 26:48.374
JESUS.

26:48.474 --> 26:51.143
I'M GONNA DO
THAT FUCKING PLAY.

26:51.243 --> 26:52.611
YOU ARE?

26:52.712 --> 26:55.648
YEAH. I'M GONNA DO IT
SO YOU CAN WATCH IT.

26:55.748 --> 26:57.884
OH, MY GOD.

27:00.086 --> 27:02.121
