HELP ME WITH THIS?

27:02.221 --> 27:04.256
HOW DO I HELP YOU?

27:04.356 --> 27:07.026
UM, HERE.

27:09.195 --> 27:10.629
SPREAD 'EM.

27:10.730 --> 27:12.899
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

27:14.166 --> 27:17.303
- Hannah: OH, MY GOD.
- ( grunts )

27:17.403 --> 27:20.206
- Adam: ALL RIGHT,
HELP ME GRAB THESE.
- OKAY, GOT IT.

27:20.306 --> 27:22.441
Hannah:
OH, MY GOD, OKAY.

27:22.541 --> 27:24.376
Adam:
ALL RIGHT, WET IT DOWN.

27:24.476 --> 27:26.979
GOT IT.

27:27.079 --> 27:29.916
WAIT.
GET A LITTLE CLOSER.

27:30.016 --> 27:31.884
- OKAY.
- THERE'S BIRD SHIT
