* RAH, RAH, RAH, RAH,
YEAH, YOU ARE *

27:54.040 --> 27:56.642
* GROWING UP,
I'M TWICE THE MAN *

27:56.743 --> 27:59.245
* YEAH, YEAH, YEAH, YEAH,
YEAH, I AM *

